headline: Palantir or Arista Networks: Goldman Sachs Selects the Better AI Stock to Buy
summary: AI has been a key driver of the bull market in recent years, and its influence continues to spread across the broader economy as more companies integrate it into their operations. GlobalData estimates that about 70% of U.S. businesses are now using AI in some capacity. The financial incentive is substantial as well.
